  "body": "### Description\n\nIt would be nice to allow to choose a different codestarts for one extension:\r\n\r\ne.g\r\n```bash\r\nquarkus create app quinoa-gradle --gradle -x=io.quarkiverse.quinoa:quarkus-quinoa,resteasy-reactive --variant=quinoa-react\r\n```\r\n\r\n- Only one codestart variant should be selected by extension for one app\r\n- You can enable multiple variants (for different extensions)\r\n- This would still include default variant for other extensions when unspecified\r\n\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
